# i18n and UX

- Korean is default, but all user-facing copy must be i18n-keyed.
- English mode must not show Korean strings.
- Mobile is touch-first, safe-area aware, and PWA-ready.
- Desktop supports exchange/admin-grade multi-panel workflows.
- High-risk money, trading, staking, betting, and withdrawal actions require confirmation UX.
